      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 10.0,
      "text": "It is currently a clear morning in Berlin-Tempelhof with a temperature of 24 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 19.155,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 15.722,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a3cbe8fe2c8"
      ],
      "end": 29.453,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 19.155,
      "text": "NVIDIA has developed a breakthrough in cooling for its largest AI machines. The new servers can operate with cooling liquid temperatures reaching up to 45 degrees Celsius."
    },
    {
      "end": 40.515,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s4",
        "s5"
      ],
      "start": 29.453,
      "text": "This thermal management allows for the scaling of frontier model training and inference clusters. As this physical infrastructure expands, major corporations are integrating these tools into their daily operations."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a58be8286fe"
      ],
      "end": 50.433,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 40.515,
      "text": "Samsung Electronics is now deploying ChatGPT Enterprise and Codex to its global workforce. This represents one of the largest enterprise scale rollouts for OpenAI to date."
    },
    {
      "end": 53.103,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 50.433,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 57.68,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 53.103,
      "text": "This afternoon will remain clear with temperatures between 24 and 27 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 60.731,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 57.68,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 66.834,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 60.731,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 76.752,
      "id": "p9",
      "index": 9,
